%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BInstant%20Evolution%26quot%3B%3A%20New%20AI%20Tool%20Can%20Design%20Robots%20From%20Scratch%20In%20Seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20researchers%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20developed%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20programme%20that%20can%20design%20robots%20from%20scratch%20in%20seconds.%20Led%20by%20Illinois-based%20Northwestern%20University%2C%20the%20team%20of%20researchers%20gave%20the%20programme%20a%20simple%20prompt%3A%20Design%20a%20robot%20that%20can%20walk%20across%20a%20flat%20surface.%20The%20team%20claimed%20that%20the%20AI%20programme%20took%20a%20mere%2026%20seconds%20to%20design%20a%20walking%20robot.%20This%20new%20AI%20programme%20is%20not%20just%20fast%2C%20but%20can%20also%20run%20on%20personal%20computers%20that%20do%20not%20have%20mind-boggling%20hardware%2C%20said%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20leap%20in%20the%20development%20of%20AI%20as%20it%20presents%20innovative%20ideas%2C%20unlike%20the%20existing%20tools%20that%20only%20mimic%20humans'%20past%20works%20without%20an%20ability%20to%20generate%20new%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20about%20the%20discovery%20has%20been%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.2305180120%5C%22%3ENational%20Academy%20of%20Sciences%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20discovered%20a%20very%20fast%20AI-driven%20design%20algorithm%20that%20bypasses%20the%20traffic%20jams%20of%20evolution%2C%20without%20falling%20back%20on%20the%20bias%20of%20human%20designers%2C%26quot%3B%20Northwestern%20University's%20Sam%20Kriegman%2C%20who%20led%20the%20work%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20university's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20told%20the%20AI%20that%20we%20wanted%20a%20robot%20that%20could%20walk%20across%20land.%20Then%20we%20simply%20pressed%20a%20button%20and%20presto!%20It%20generated%20a%20blueprint%20for%20a%20robot%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%20that%20looks%20nothing%20like%20any%20animal%20that%20has%20ever%20walked%20the%20earth.%20I%20call%20this%20process%20'instant%20evolution'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AI%20programme%20evaluated%20the%20design%2C%20found%20defects%2C%20and%20chipped%20away%20at%20the%20simulated%20block%20to%20alter%20its%20structure%20with%20each%20updated%20version.%20The%20virtual%20robot%20eventually%20developed%20the%20ability%20to%20bounce%2C%20hop%2C%20and%20shuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20research%20in%20quest%20to%20explore%20the%20potential%20of%20artificial%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20itself%20is%20unassuming%20-%20small%2C%20squishy%20and%20misshapen.%20And%2C%20for%20now%2C%20it%20is%20made%20of%20inorganic%20materials.%20But%20Mr%20Kriegman%20said%20it%20represents%20the%20first%20step%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20AI-designed%20tools%20that%2C%20like%20animals%2C%20can%20act%20directly%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20look%20at%20this%20robot%2C%20they%20might%20see%20a%20useless%20gadget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20brand-new%20organism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697175660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fac1j7bo8_ai-developed-robot-1200_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Finstant-evolution-new-ai-tool-can-design-robots-from-scratch-in-seconds-4477014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20artificial%20intelligence%20programme%20created%20a%20virtual%20robot%20that%20could%20bounce%2C%20hop%2C%20and%20shuffle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Finstant-evolution-new-ai-tool-can-design-robots-from-scratch-in-seconds-4477014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2F