re%20else%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20buildings%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20including%20many%20occupied%20by%20civilians%2C%20that%20rescue%20services%20were%20struggling%20to%20reach%20new%20bomb%20sites%20quickly.%20Hamdan%20said%20he%20was%20attending%20about%2010%20calls%20a%20day%2C%20some%20lasting%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplosions%20from%20air%20strikes%20echo%20every%20few%20minutes%20-%20killing%20more%20than%201%2C500%20people%20in%20Gaza%20so%20far%20including%20hundreds%20of%20children%2C%20local%20health%20authorities%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoads%20cratered%20from%20direct%20hits%20or%20blocked%20by%20rubble%20from%20nearby%20strikes%20hinder%20progress%20and%20initial%20rescue%20work%20is%20often%20done%20by%20neighbours%20pulling%20away%20chunks%20of%20debris%20in%20search%20of%20survivors%20or%20hoping%20to%20retrieve%20bodies%20for%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELacking%20enough%20heavy%20machinery%20such%20as%20mechanical%20diggers%20and%20bulldozers%2C%20rescue%20workers%20also%20rely%20on%20shovels%20and%20other%20tools%20they%20wield%20by%20hand%20to%20pull%20away%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20emotional%20toll%20has%20been%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamdan%2C%2039%2C%20has%20a%20bandage%20on%20his%20left%20hand%20and%20wrist%2C%20injured%20by%20falling%20debris%20during%20a%20rescue%20attempt%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20he%20was%20only%20able%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20bodies%20of%20two%20girls%2C%20dead%20in%20the%20ruins%20of%20their%20home%20in%20the%20south%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20where%20he%20is%20based%20with%20his%20team%20of%2012%20other%20government%20rescue%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20stop%20thinking%20about%20my%20own%20four%20daughters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20that%20keeps%20him%20going%20is%20the%20hope%20of%20finding%20more%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20four%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20emergency%20medical%20workers%20were%20killed%20when%20their%20ambulances%20were%20hit%20in%20two%20different%20incidents.%20Their%20colleagues%20clung%20to%20each%20other%20afterwards%2C%20shaking%20with%20sobs%2C%20video%20posted%20by%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20Hamdan's%20own%20team%20were%20injured%20by%20flying%20glass%20when%20an%20air%20strike%20blew%20the%20windows%20out%20of%20their%20ambulance%20in%20Khan%20Younis%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20said.%20Neither%20is%20badly%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAshraf%20Al-Qidra%2C%20the%20spokesman%20of%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%2010%20medical%20staffers%20had%20been%20killed%20so%20far%20and%2014%20health%20facilities%20damaged%2C%20including%20the%20lone%20hospital%20in%20Beit%20Hanoun%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20armed%20forces%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20about%20strikes%20injuring%20rescuers%20and%20medics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESLEEPLESS%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESnatching%20little%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20of%20sleep%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20no%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20over%20a%20day%20and%20night%2C%20Hamdan%20and%20the%20others%20in%20his%20team%20barely%20have%20time%20to%20eat%20or%20phone%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20so%20frightened%20that%20at%20some%20point%20I%20will%20get%20a%20call%20to%20head%20out%20to%20a%20rescue%20and%20it%20will%20be%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamdan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamdan%20tries%20to%20talk%20to%20his%20wife%20and%20six%20children%20aged%20from%20his%20daughter%20Maisa%2C%2013%2C%20down%20to%20baby%20son%20Muhannad%2C%20between%20rescues%2C%20using%20video%20calls%20to%20see%20their%20faces.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20going%20blind%20until%20I%20make%20that%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20previous%20wars%2C%20Israel%20often%20gave%20a%20few%20minutes%20notice%20to%20residents%20of%20blocks%20it%20intended%20to%20target%20but%20Gaza%20residents%20say%20it%20has%20not%20done%20so%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20war%20is%20harsh%20beyond%20imagining.%20They%20are%20collapsing%20people's%20buildings%20without%20warning.%20They%20knock%20down%20high-rise%20buildings%20on%20top%20of%20their%20residents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hamdan%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20through%20repeated%20wars%20since%20becoming%20a%20rescuer%20for%20the%20Gaza%20government%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20Reuters%20video%20a%20missile%20could%20be%20seen%20ploughing%20into%20the%20base%20of%20a%2010-storey%20building%20in%20Gaza%20City%20on%20Thursday%2C%20causing%20a%20massive%20explosion%20as%20the%20surrounding%20area%20was%20engulfed%20in%20a%20cloud%20of%20smoke%20and%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20medical%20worker%20Rami%20Ali%20was%20shown%20in%20a%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20video%20sitting%20in%20an%20ambulance%20crying%20into%20his%20hand%2C%20his%20body%20heaving%2C%20after%20watching%20the%20bodies%20of%20children%20being%20taken%20from%20a%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamdan%20works%20for%20the%20Civil%20Emergency%20department%2C%20the%20fire%20and%20rescue%20service%20operated%20by%20the%20Gaza%20government%2C%20which%20Hamas%20has%20controlled%20since%20seizing%20power%20in%20the%20enclave%20during%20a%20brief%20Palestinian%20civil%20war%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20have%20repeatedly%20clashed%20during%20that%20time%2C%20with%20air%20strikes%20hitting%20targets%20in%20Gaza.%20Hamdan%20said%20that%20as%20in%20previous%20violence%2C%20the%20civil%20emergency%20team%20was%20currently%20operating%20out%20of%20schools%2C%20believing%20them%20to%20be%20safer%20from%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20on%20alert%20all%20the%20time.%20There%20is%20bombing%20everywhere.%20There%20are%20injured%20and%20martyrs%20everywhere.%20So%20if%20I%20get%20one%20hour%20sleep%20I%20will%20be%20happy%2C%26quot