20among%20the%20Palestinian%20population.%20No%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%E2%80%9D%20any%20more%2C%20but%20rather%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20end%20of%20the%20occupation%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20young%20people%20evoke%20%E2%80%9Cresistance%2C%20by%20all%20means%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20context%20in%20which%20Hamas%20carried%20out%20its%20attack.%20And%20the%20militant%20organisation%20used%20this%20despair%20to%20legitimise%20itself%20and%20win%20the%20support%20of%20a%20section%20of%20Palestinian%20public%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaza%2C%20an%20open-air%20prison%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Hamas%20operates%2C%202.3%C2%A0million%20Palestinians%20are%20crammed%20into%20365%20km%3Csup%3E2%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20making%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20densely%20populated%20territories.%20More%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Ffr%2Fstory%2F2022%2F09%2F1127031%5C%22%3Etwo%20thirds%20of%20the%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20live%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20and%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Israeli%20NGO%20B'Tselem%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplateforme-palestine.org%2FGaza-les-chiffres-cles-2023%5C%22%3Eunemployment%20rate%20is%2075%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20people%20under%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%202007%2C%20this%20territory%20has%20also%20been%20subject%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fproche-orient%2Farticle%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2Fa-gaza-des-bateaux-palestiniens-contre-la-nouvelle-barriere-maritime-voulue-par-israel_5306341_3218.html%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20blockade%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20sea%2C%20air%20and%20land%2C%20which%20almost%20entirely%20deprives%20it%20of%20contact%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGazans%20are%20regularly%20cut%20off%20from%20water%20and%20electricity%2C%20and%20depend%20mainly%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Ffr%2Fopinionfr%2Fpalestine-israel-aide-inte