0wall%20have%20been%20built%20between%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20and%20Israel.%20This%20security%20wall%20was%20supposed%20to%20follow%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGreen_Line_(Israel)%5C%22%3E315km%20green%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20outlined%20in%20the%201947%20UN%20partition%20plan%2C%20but%20the%20past%20years%20have%20seen%20it%20snake%20on%20and%20on%2C%20gradually%20encroaching%20on%20Palestinian%20territory%20and%20isolating%20certain%20Palestinian%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20Palestinian%20MP%20told%20me%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20the%20Arab%20Wailing%20Wall%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20others%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CWall%20of%20Shame%E2%80%9D.%20Even%20East%20Jerusalem%20is%20increasingly%20occupied%2C%20including%20the%20Esplanade%20of%20the%20Mosques%2C%20home%20to%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Mosque%2C%20Islam's%20third-holiest%20site.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20name%20that%20the%20Hamas%20gave%20to%20its%20attack%2C%20%E2%80%9COperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%E2%80%9D%2C%20shows%20just%20how%20the%20Islamist%20group%20has%20managed%20to%20act%20as%20a%20soundboard%20to%20the%20population's%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDaily%20despair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20freedom%20of%20movement%20of%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20is%20extremely%20limited%20%E2%80%93%20they%20depend%20entirely%20on%20permits%20obtained%20from%20the%20Israeli%20authorities.%20Every%20day%2C%20Palestinians%20have%20to%20laboriously%20cross%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.openedition.org%2Fpup%2F8020%3Flang%3Dfr%5C%22%3Echeckpoints%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20children%20explain%20to%20me%20that%20they%20cross%20the%20checkpoint%20between%20Abu%20Dis%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Jerusalem%20to%20go%20to%20school%3B%20they%20go%20alone%20because%20their%20parents%20don't%20have%20the%20necessary%20permits%20and%20spend%20at%20least%20an%20hour%20there%20every%20day.%20Older%20students%20tell%20me%20that%20they%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20to%20their%20university%2C%20but%20now%20there's%20the%20wall%20and%20a%20checkpoint.%20The%20UN%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fin-facts-and-figures%2F%5C%22%3E593%20checkpoints%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mostly%20designed%20to%20protect%20Israeli%20settlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20situation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20is%20also%20deplorable.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Functad.org%2Fnews%2Feconomic-restrictions-west-bank-exact-50-billion-toll-between-2000-and-2020%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20and%20goods%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20bans%20on%20the%20importation%20of%20certain%20technologies%20and%20inputs%2C%20bureaucratic%20controls%2C%20checkpoints%2C%20gates%2C%20earth%20mounds%2C%20roadblocks%20and%20trenches%20%E2%80%93%20are%20choking%20development.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Ffr%2Fstory%2F2022%2F09%2F1127031%5C%22%3Epoverty%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20at%2036%25%20and%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20at%2026%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20Netanyahu%20government%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euronews.com%2F2023%2F07%2F03%2Fisraeli-strikes-in-the-occupied-west-bank-kill-at-least-eight%5C%22%3Estepped%20up%20its%20interventions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20preventive%20raids.%20Before%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20200%20Palestinians%20had%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Ffr%2Fstory%2F2023%2F05%2F1134792%5C%22%3EUN%20counts%3C%2Fa%3E%204%2C900%20Palestinian%20political%20prisoners%20and%20notes%20the%20deplorable%20conditions%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%20and%20the%20ill-treatment%20inflicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20deadlock%2C%20latent%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdded%20to%20all%20this%20is%20the%20political%20impasse.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20elections%20in%20Palestine%20since%202006.%20The%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20recognised%20as%20the%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20has%20become%20an%20empty%20shell%20with%20no%20real%20power.%20Power%20is%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%2087-year-old%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20who%20has%20lost%20the%20support%20of%20his%20people.%20After%20the%20repeated%20failure%20of%20negotiations%20between%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20and%20Israel%2C%20some%20even%20consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iris-france.org%2F168899-palestine-biden-hypocrite-abbas-complice%2F%5C%22%3EMahmoud%20Abbas%20to%20be%20an%20accomplice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2021%2F12%2F10%2F1063171482%2Fpalestinian-dissidents-rally-against-corruption-in-the-palestinian-authority%5C%22%3ECorruption%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20paralysing%20all%20Palestinian%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20no%20longer%20expects%20anything%20from%20politics%20and%20even%20less%20from%20negotiations.%20Since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20resurgence%20of%20%E2%80%9Clone%20wolf%E2%80%9D%20attacks%20driven%20by%20despair.%20Like%20the%20Palestinian%20driver%20who%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lorientlejour.com%2Farticle%2F1347957%2Fattaque-a-un-checkpoint-en-cisjordanie-occupee-trois-blesses.html%5C%22%3Eploughed%20into%20a%20group%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20he%20was%20about%20to%20cross%20a%20checkpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20same%20despair%20that%20drives%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20to%20rally%20around%20Hamas's%20cruel%20attacks%20today.%20As%20Elie%20Barnavi%20points%20out%2C%20we%20could%20even%20fear%20the%20outbreak%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Fopinion%2Farticle%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Felie-barnavi-the-hamas-attack-is-the-result-of-the-combination-of-a-fanatical-islamist-organization-and-an-idiotic-israeli-policy_6157666_23.html%5C%22%3Enew%20intifada%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas'%20rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Hamas%20has%20been%20able%20to%20weaponise%20these%20sentiments%20and%20so%20affirm%20itself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctrue%20defender%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20the%20militant%20group%20won%20the%20Palestinian%20legislative%20elections.%20Despite%20the%20democratic%20nature%20of%20these%20elections%2C%20the%20result%20was%20not%20recognised%20by%20the%20international%20community%2C%20which%20refused%20to%20allow%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20to%20take%20power.%20Hamas%20therefore%20fell%20back%20onto%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20of%20which%20it%20took%20control.%20From%20Gaza%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20radicalise%20and%20delegitimise%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20and%20waited%20for%20momentum%20to%20build%20before%20putting%20its%20words%20into%20action.%20In%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20this%20moment%20has%20arrived.%20The%20leaders%20no%20doubt%20felt%20that%20the%20context%20was%20favourable%20for%20a%20large-scale%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fisraels-netanyahu-facing-off-against-the-supreme-court-and-proposing-to-limit-judicial-independence-and-3-other-threats-to-israeli-democracy-197096%5C%22%3Einternal%20destabilisation%20in%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20a%20breach%20of%20which%20Hamas%20could%20take%20advantage.%20Never%20has%20Israel%20been%20as%20divided%20as%20it%20has%20been%20since%20the%20arrival%20of%20Netanyahu's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fa-stunning-political-comeback-for-israels-netanyahu-may-give-way-to-gov