20morning%2C%20an%20airstrike%20targeted%20a%20charity%20organisation%20directly%20behind%20the%20building.%20The%20building%20was%20partially%20destroyed%2C%20but%20Ms%20Barzak%20and%20the%20others%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-tactical-challenges-for-israel-as-its-troops-prep-to-enter-gaza-strip-4474896%5C%22%3E5%20Challenges%20For%20Israel%20If%20They%20Enter%20Gaza%2C%20And%20Lessons%20From%20Ukraine%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20afternoon%2C%20we%20received%20three%20phone%20calls%20from%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Army%2C%20ordering%20us%20to%20evacuate%20our%20building%20immediately%20and%20go%20to%20a%20place%20at%20least%20one%20kilometer%20away%20from%20the%20Islamic%20University%2C%20either%20north%20or%20south.%20We%20packed%20our%20bags%20and%20left%20everything%20else%20behind.%20We%20evacuated%20with%20our%20relatives%20who%20lived%20one%20block%20away%20from%20us%20to%20our%20uncle's%20house%20in%20the%20Gaza%20City%20centre%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Barzak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20way%20to%20their%20uncle's%20house%2C%20Ms%20Barzak%2C%20her%20husband%20Hazem%2C%20a%20lawyer%20with%20the%20International%20Commission%20For%20Human%20Rights%20(ICHR)%2C%2012-year-old%20son%20Karim%20and%20their%20relatives%20witnessed%20the%20true%20scale%20of%20the%20devastation.%20With%20people%20fleeing%20in%20all%20directions%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20bombs%20going%20off%20and%20Israeli%20jets%20flying%20overhead%2C%20there%20was%20no%20place%20that%20felt%20safe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Barzaks%20arrived%20at%20their%20uncle's%20house%20but%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20the%20brutal%20airstrikes%20began.%20The%20families%20huddled%20together%20in%20one%20room%2C%20listening%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20bombs%20exploding%20and%20buildings%20collapsing%20in%20what%20was%20a%20%26quot%3B12-hour%20nightm