s%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Hamas'%20deadliest%20attack%20on%20Israel%20in%20decades%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20had%20a%20reason%20to%20cry.%20My%20son%20lost%20his%20pets%2C%20my%20nieces%20lost%20their%20friends%2C%20my%20nephew%20lost%20six%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20my%20cousins%20and%20friends%20became%20homeless%2C%20and%20lost%20their%20families.%20We%20are%20all%20broken%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20once-thriving%20downtown%20Gaza%20now%20lies%20in%20ruins%2C%20a%20vast%20expanse%20of%20rubble%20where%20once%20stood%20educational%2C%20health%2C%20civic%2C%20commercial%2C%20and%20governmental%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas%20after%20its%20attack%20left%201%2C200%20Israelis%20dead%20in%20its%20wake.%20Six%20days%20since%20the%20Hamas%20onslaught%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20bombard%20the%20densely%20populated%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20artillery%20shells%20and%20airstrikes%2C%20preparing%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20augment%20the%20combined%20might%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%20(IDF)%20and%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%2C%203%20lakh%20reservists%20have%20also%20joined%20Prime%20Minister%20Netanyahu's%20quest%20to%20pulverise%20the%20362-square-kilometre%20sliver%20of%20land%20that%20the%20Gazans%20call%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Nakba'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20without%20electricity%20after%20its%20only%20power%20plant%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20power%20and%20no%20water.%20We%20are%20using%20cellular%20data%2C%20but%20it%20is%20barely%20enough%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20use%20WhatsApp.%20We%20can%20still%20get%20groceries%20from%20a%20mini-market%20nearby%2C%20but%20that%20is%20all.%20No%20NGOs%20or%20United%20Nations%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20us%2C%20and%20there%