0Israel.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAircraft%20carriers%20have%20long%20been%20deployed%20to%20show%20strength%20and%20deter%20hostile%20forces.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECarrier%20strike%20groups%20host%20significant%20airpower%20and%20firepower%2C%20and%20the%20Ford's%20new%20technological%20capabilities%20make%20it%20a%20major%20presence.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy's%20newest%2C%20largest%2C%20and%20most%20advanced%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20the%20accompanying%20escort%20ships%20in%20its%20strike%20group%20are%20in%20position%20in%20waters%20near%20Israel%2C%20bringing%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20firepower%20and%20a%20powerful%20presence%20to%20an%20area%20grappling%20with%20instability%20and%20tragedy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20Gerald%20R.%20Ford%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20led%20by%20the%20eponymous%20first-in-class%20US%20Navy%20supercarrier%20on%20its%20first%20full%20deployment%20and%20boasting%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20new%20technologies%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-newest-supercarrier-deployment-unexpected-turn-israel-crisis-2023-10%5C%22%3Earrived%20in%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20announced%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20carrier%20strike%20group%20toward%20Israel%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20day%20after%20Hamas%20carried%20out%20deadly%20terror%20attacks%20against%20the%20US%20ally.%20The%20Ford's%20sudden%20retasking%20was%20presented%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20US%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20deterrent%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20task%20for%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20which%20have%20long%20been%20used%20to%20project%20American%20military%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ships%20sailing%20with%20the%20Ford%20include%20the%20Ticonderoga-class%20guided-missile%20cruiser%20USS%20Normandy%20and%20the%20Arleigh-Burke-class%20guided-missile%20destroyers%20USS%20Thomas%20Hudner%2C%20USS%20Ramage