he%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20address%20all%20of%20our%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPack%20your%20home%20and%20take%20it%20anywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20of%20ODF%20Group%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323054%2Fbengaluru-architects-build-zero-waste-sustainable-euroschool-near-national-park%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitect%20behind%20the%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Majid%20says%20that%20while%20people%20in%20Kerala%20still%20prefer%20traditional%20homes%2C%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20government%2C%20people%20are%20widening%20their%20horizons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201381px)%20100vw%2C%201381px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221381%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20is%20made%20using%20Light%20Gauge%20Steel%20Frame%20(LGSF)%20technology%2C%20which%20uses%20cold-formed%20steel%20as%20the%20primary%20construction%20material.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110.jpg%201381w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG_20220324_174231-1-1-2-1-1-1697118110-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332114%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22777%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20made%20using%20Light%20Gauge%20Steel%20Frame%20(LGSF)%20technology%2C%20which%20uses%20cold-formed%20steel%20as%20the%20primary%20construction%20material.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20ODF%20Group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20India%20are%20not%20quite%20aware%20of%20the%20technology.%20However%2C%20in%20Kerala%2C%20after%20the%202009%20floods%2C%20the%20people%20there%20have%20been%20on%20a%20hunt%20to%20find%20alternative%20methods%20to%20build%20their%20homes.%20After%20the%20floods%2C%20people%20realised%20how%20any%20kind%20of%20home%20could%20be%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERestoring%20such%20homes%20can%20be%20very%20expensive%20and%20time-consuming.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20resources%20are%20used%20to%20reconstruct%20or%20repair%20these%20homes%20such%20as%20mortar%20and%20it%20also%20causes%20a%20lot%20of%20wastage.%20LGSF%20technology%20is%20great%20in%20that%20respect%20as%20it%20gives%20the%20house%20a%20high%20strength-to-weight%20ratio%2C%20making%20them%20more%20resilient%20to%20forces%20such%20as%20earthquakes%2C%20hurricanes%2C%20and%20heavy%20winds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20people%20are%20sceptical%20about%20it%2C%20we%20have%20already%20made%20a%20few%20homes%20using%20the%20technology%20in%20Kerala%20and%20are%20soon%20planning%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpand%20to%20Karnataka%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Tamil%20Nadu%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Dr%20Jayakumar%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20Majid%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20beautiful%20home%20and%20the%20client%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20as%20cosy%20as%20it%20can%20be.%20The%20plot%20is%20on%20two%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ground%20level%20was%20utilised%20for%20parking%20space%20and%20the%20upper%20level%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20home.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20months%20for%20the%20home%20to%20complete.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20structure%20and%20planning%20were%20done%20in%20just%20a%20month%20and%20since%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20house%20was%20quite%20detailed%20it%20took%20us%20another%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20complete%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complete%20construction%20of%20the%20house%20cost%20Dr%20Jayakumar%20just%20about%20Rs%2080%20lakhs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStep-by-step%20guide%20to%20LGSF%20homes%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20way%20the%20technology%20works%2C%20Majid%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20step%20to%20building%20an%20LGSF%20home%20is%20to%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20customer%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20structure.%20The%20architect%20then%20presents%20the%20preliminary%20sketching%20and%20designing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20design%20is%20done%2C%20it%20is%20moved%20to%20the%20structure%20team.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20team%20makes%20the%20drawings%20and%20finalises%20the%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20structure%20plan%20is%20ready%2C%20we%20can%20actually%20get%20a%20tentative%20cost%20of%20the%20house.%20Since%20very%20little%20manual%20labour%20is%20involved%2C%20most%20of%20the%20cost%20comes%20from%20the%20material.%20Hence%2C%20once%20the%20structure%20is%20ready%2C%20we%20take%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20customer%20and%20then%20finalise%20the%20deal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20the%20step%20of%20fabrication.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20factories%2C%20the%20steel%20frames%20are%20fabricated%20using%20advanced%20mac