ace%20Centre%20in%20Sriharikota%2C%20with%20ISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20confirming%20the%20successful%20launch.%20Millions%20of%20Indians%20across%20the%20country%20watched%20this%20historic%20event%20live%2C%20and%20behind%20the%20chairman%2C%20two%20key%20figures%20of%20the%20mission%20stood%20%E2%80%94%20Mohana%20Kumar%2C%20the%20mission%20director%2C%20and%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20project%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%2C%20the%20cynosure%20of%20all%20eyes%2C%20stood%20with%20a%20composed%20demeanour%2C%20smiling%20and%20applauding%20as%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20years%20of%20dedication%20paid%20off.%20Meanwhile%2C%20more%20than%20250%20kilometres%20away%20in%20Viluppuram%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20his%20proud%20family%20celebrated%20with%20fireworks%20and%20sweets%20at%20the%2046-year-old%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20working%20on%20Gaganyaan%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20manned%20mission%20to%20space%2C%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%20recently%20said%20at%20an%20event%20that%20they%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20launch.%20%E2%80%9CGaganyaan%20programme%20is%20coming%20up.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20human%20exploration%20programme.%20We%20have%20the%20roadmap%20and%20we%20will%20have%20the%20launch%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20test%20flight%20of%20Gaganyaan%20is%20scheduled%20for%2021%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20an%20average%20student%20to%20a%20topper%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20635px)%20100vw%2C%20635px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22P%20Veeramuthuvel%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830.jpg%20635w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830-300x213.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830-500x354.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMuthuvel-1697118830-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332136%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EP%20Veeramuthuvel%20found%20his%20calling%20after%20engineering%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20modest%20background%2C%20Veeramuthuvel%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20at%20ISRO%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20his%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%20was%20raised%20in%20the%20railway%20quarters%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F154149%2Fisro-scientist-chandrayaan-annadurai-tamil-nadu-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EViluppuram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20his%20father%20Palanivel%20worked%20as%20a%20technician%20for%20the%20Southern%20Railway.%20He%20studied%20in%20a%20government%20school%20called%20the%20Railway%20Mixed%20High%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20an%20average%20student%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20to%20do%20after%20school.%20My%20parents%20did%20not%20have%20much%20education%3B%20there%20was%20no%20one%20to%20guide%20me%20in%20my%20higher%20studies.%20So%20after%20discussing%20with%20my%20friends%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20an%20engineering%20diploma%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Veeramuthuvel%20in%20a%20video%20he%20released%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EDTNext%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Palanivel%20said%20that%20Veeramuthuvel%20is%20the%20first%20graduate%20in%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20Veer