%20learn%20the%20art%20of%20natural%20dyes%20and%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20a%20natural%20dyer%20in%20Ahmedabad%20who%20offered%20me%20an%20exciting%20barter.%20I%20would%20develop%20a%20website%20for%20them%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20they%20would%20teach%20me%20how%20to%20dye%20clothes%20naturally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20month%20of%20training%2C%20Alankrutha%20was%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20basics%20of%20natural%20dyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20was%20clear%20to%20me%20was%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313885%2Fhyderabad-manya-cherabuddi-makes-natural-dyes-conducts-workshops-sustainable-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20dyeing%20is%20an%20art.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20is%20not%20something%20mechanical%20that%20any%20person%20can%20do.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20beauty%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20engage%20the%20small%20community%20of%20natural%20dyers%20present%20in%20the%20making%20of%20my%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20collaborating%20with%20NGOs%20and%20farmers%20that%20send%20unbleached%20organic%20fabric%20to%20make%20the%20garment%20and%20dye%20them%20naturally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%20food%2C%20natural%20clothing%20and%20farm%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Elephant%20In%20You%2C%20the%20couple%20sells%20a%20ready-to-wear%20collection%20such%20as%20shirts%2C%20dresses%2C%20hoodies%20and%20bottoms%20in%20unbleached%20organic%20cotton%2C%20linen%20and%20hemp%20fabrics%20that%20use%20natural%20dyes.%20However%2C%20clothing%20was%20one%20part%20of%20a%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20Alankrutha%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20helps%20people%20live%20sustainably.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20cover%20the%20three%20essent