ner%E2%80%99s%20support%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20take%20this%20step.%20To%20everyone%20else%2C%20it%20seemed%20crazy%20to%20leave%20our%20lives%20in%20the%20US%20and%20come%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20I%20was%20not%20happy%20with%20my%20job%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20of%20my%20own.%20The%20pandemic%20made%20the%20need%20to%20move%20urgent%20for%20me.%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20the%20right%20time%20for%20me%20to%20transform%20our%20lives%20and%20live%20sustainably%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Alankrutha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20why%20she%20named%20her%20brand%20Elephant%20in%20You%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20friend%20who%20makes%20handmade%20paper%2C%20she%20started%20to%20talk%20about%20elephants.%20It%20was%20a%20fascinating%20conversation%20as%20she%20told%20me%20how%20elephants%2C%20although%20the%20biggest%20animals%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20never%20bring%20an%20imbalance%20in%20the%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20feed%20on%20large%20amounts%20of%20veggies%20but%20keep%20moving%20to%20different%20areas%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20exhaust%20one%20area%E2%80%99s%20resources.%20Their%20excreta%20also%20nourishes%20the%20ground%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20for%20plants%20to%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20she%20believes%20humans%20should%20live%20in%20society.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20you%20take%20from%20nature%2C%20take%20it%20in%20a%20reasonable%20way%20and%20do%20not%20destroy%20it%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20idea%20that%20humans%20should%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%20just%20as%20elephants%20do%20in%20a%20forest%20is%20what%20gave%20the%20brand%20its%20name.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20