20in%20an%20exhibition.%20Alankrutha%E2%80%99s%20designs%20and%20clothes%20are%20very%20good%20and%20trendy.%20They%20are%20all%20organic%20and%20sustainable.%20The%20material%20and%20tailoring%20feels%20good%20on%20the%20skin.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20they%20not%20only%20deal%20in%20organic%20cotton%20but%20also%20hemp%20and%20linen%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20three%20years%20of%20moving%20to%20India%20and%20setting%20up%20the%20brand%20have%20been%20transformative%20for%20the%20couple.%20Looking%20back%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20brand%20is%20a%20reminder%20to%20society%20that%20we%20need%20to%20give%20back%20to%20nature%20as%20well.%20We%20have%20to%20stop%20producing%20waste%20and%20try%20to%20live%20a%20slow%20and%20sustainable%20life.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20living%20sustainably%20now%2C%20we%20will%20lose%20the%20amazing%20resources%20that%20nature%20has%20to%20offer.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696948290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alankrutha%20Chandra%20and%20her%20husband%20Meher%20Gundavarum%20decided%20to%20embrace%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%20They%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20started%20'Elephant%20In%20You'%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20brand%20that%20covers%20three%20essentials%20of%20living%20%E2%80%94%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Woke%20Up%20In%20The%20Hospital%E2%80%99%3A%20It%20Took%20Everything%20For%20Me%20to%20Fight%20Depression%20%26amp%3B%20Rebuild%20Myself%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20suicide.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaikishaan%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%2